    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Fuinjutsu </p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 7 (Spell Level 4)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 8</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 21 | <b>Successes:</b> 3</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 9 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 22</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>This useful technique sheathes your hand in a faint purple glow that coalesces into a seal when the target is touched by it, sealing away their ability to make any sound with their voice (including grunts, moans, whispers, etc.). The seal disappears if the target dies.</p>\n\n\n\n",
